  "texts": [
    "This unexpected generalization capacity indicates that the models effectively adjusted to various imaging conditions or patient demographics present in the external dataset.",
    "Although our proposed fine-tuning method yields promising results in enhancing landmark detection accuracy, several limitations require consideration.",
    "First, we adopted DiffDRR to generate simulated X-ray images for our evaluation.",
    "These images may not fully reflect the noise, artifacts, and variations in imaging that are present in real intraoperative fluoroscopy.",
    "16 The effectiveness of our method on clinical images has yet to be confirmed."
  ]
}